main event: A white elongated object was observed in Concord, New Hampshire, moving at 'unbelievable' speed and suddenly disappeared without fading away slowly.
interesting points: The object was observed for 8-10 seconds and had a high rate of speed
It emitted pulsing lights as it passed through the sky
The object disappeared suddenly at a definite point without fading away slowly
The report mentions a strange white mass about the object, and the witness describes it as quiet and maneuverable
The witness estimated the object to be about 6 feet in diameter and 2-3 feet high
